      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LETHAL FORCE (2) was quickly into stride and found the front last start to record an all-the-way win (24.10) at this track in a Grade 5 over 425m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Expected to go well again. BEELINE (7) used the rails draw to advantage to get home last time at this track and distance (23.99), scoring by 7 lengths. Expecting another good run. MISS BARBIE (1) has been in super consistent form, finishing in the minors at her last four runs. Last time finished 2nd on March 18 over 425m at this track behind Rae's Rainbow beaten 0.8 lengths (24.46) in a Bottom Up - Restricted Win. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Racing well and deserves a win. COSMIC REWARD (3) is building a nice sequence of placings and will be thereabouts again.",
